  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u2013   \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b90\u0b8f \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka made a foolish bet on Chinese investments \u2013 CIA chief",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "CIA chief Phil Barnes said that Sri Lanka made a foolish bet on Chinese investments",
        "Bill Barnes, the head of America's CIA, said that Sri Lanka, a South Asian country, foolishly bet on China's investments.",
        "For the past few months, Sri Lanka has faced food fuel shortages, prolonged power outages and rising inflation due to lack of foreign exchange to import essential goods.",
        "In this situation, the CIA chief mentions that China's high debt investments made by Sri Lankan leaders are the reason for the decline of the South Asian country's economy. He also says that China has the strength to project itself and the ability to attract investment.",
        "The world countries should think about a country like Sri Lanka which has got a huge debt from China. Sri Lanka has foolishly bet on its economic future due to which the country has faced disastrous consequences politically and economically, said the CIA chief."
      ],
